That's the full flow: your documents get ingested once into ChromaDB, and every time you ask a question, it gets embedded, matched against your stored chunks (with the keyword-boost fix for code/config files), and the retrieved context gets handed to Llama3 to generate a grounded answer.
                                                                                                                                                               
